Package ss.pentago.model.board

Enum Quadrant

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Quadrant>
      • ss.pentago.model.board.Quadrant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Quadrant>
    public enum Quadrant
extends java.lang.Enum<Quadrant>
    Quadrant represents one of four sub boards of Board. Each Quadrant has an appropriate offset, which can be used to deal with the fields in that sub board.
